name: ROCKET FRENZYY!!
description:
This is ROCKET FRENZY!! A game where you have to complete levels to go to next level and if you die you have to replay the current level..

The game has Rockets and Meteors with explosions and a great background music to chill to..

THE GAME IS FOR WINDOWS(PC) AND MAC ONLY FOR NOW ..

ANDROID RELEASE WILL BE COMING SOON..

The game has 50 levels and each level will get interesting and difficult and quite annoying if you go on completing the level..

This is my first game so I wasn't able to create a great UI but the gameplay is fun and exciting!!

So set your engines and take off into the space with ROCKET FRENZY!! and enjoy the fun ride ..

The game is created by SaturnswampGames..
